Comment: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:31.73,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,===ED-CN===
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:31.73,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}看见谁都无法看见的梦{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:37.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}舍弃所有不需要的事物{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}无法割舍的感情{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:46.05,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}深藏在我的心里{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:52.52,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}依然处在现实与理想的夹缝中{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:57.72,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}即使牺牲的枷锁 栓住我的脚{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:02.86,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}无法压抑满腔的冲动{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:09.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}因为我有一颗强烈追求的心{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:15.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}虚伪 恐惧 虚饰 忧愁{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:21.05,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}面对各种负面情绪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:26.56,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}我也不会弱到被击垮{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:31.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}不知孤独为何物 Trickster{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:39.53,Sub,,0,0,0,,秘密会议
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:43.27,Sub,,0,0,0,,听起来好像他们每周五都会进行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:44.87,Sub,,0,0,0,,BINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:47.97,Sub,,0,0,0,,今天的我可要立大功了
